program: PRE LBRACE LPAREN FALSE RBRACE
##
## Ends in an error in state: 33.
##
## formula -> formula . IFF formula [ WEDGE VEE RPAREN IMP IFF ]
## formula -> formula . IMP formula [ WEDGE VEE RPAREN IMP IFF ]
