program: PRE LBRACE IDENT WHILE
##
## Ends in an error in state: 35.
##
## formula -> term . EQ term [ WEDGE VEE RPAREN RBRACE IMP IFF ]
## formula -> term . NEQ_LOG term [ WEDGE VEE RPAREN RBRACE IMP IFF ]
## formula -> term . LT term [ WEDGE VEE RPAREN RBRACE IMP IFF ]
