program: PRE LBRACE FALSE RPAREN
##
## Ends in an error in state: 45.
##
## formula -> formula . IFF formula [ WEDGE VEE RBRACE IMP IFF ]
## formula -> formula . IMP formula [ WEDGE VEE RBRACE IMP IFF ]
## formula -> formula . VEE formula [ WEDGE VEE RBRACE IMP IFF ]
