## cmd_node -> WHILE . bexpr INVARIANT LBRACE formula RBRACE DO cmd END [ SEMI POST END ELSE ]
##
## The known suffix of the stack is as follows:
## WHILE
##

expected a boolean condition

Note: a `while` is shaped `while cond invariant { I } do ... end`. The condition is built from comparisons (`x < n`), connectives `and`, `or`, `not`, and parentheses.

